<h2>About</h2>
<p>
    This portal enables residents to report issues, receive updates, and participate in improving municipal services.
    It is designed to be simple, mobile-friendly, and inclusive.
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Report issues like water leaks, potholes, electricity faults, and sanitation problems.</li>
    <li>Attach photos or PDFs to help our teams resolve matters faster.</li>
    <li>Future features: local events & announcements, service request status tracking.</li>
</ul>
<p>For assistance email <a href="mailto:support@municipality.gov">support@municipality.gov</a>.</p>
